item.title: How Do Relationships Affect Testosterone Levels? ~ Milica Jelenic
item.description: The Pleasure Zone with Milica Jelenic - Diamond Host In recent years there have been studies that measure testosterone levels in cis men and women who are in relationships. There are some interesting findings on how testosterone is affected by relationships and I am excited to share some of that research with you on this episode... item.title: WR Rankings: Top Performers, Potential Breakouts & Hidden Gems (Ep. 110)
item.description: Join Scott Bogman, Pat Fitzmaurice, and Alfredo Brown (@ThePretendGM) from Footballguys as they dissect the top 36 consensus dynasty WR rankings and discuss how their personal rankings compare. From Justin Jefferson to John Metchie III, they lay out comprehensive analysis of the elites, the breakouts, the sleepers, and the busts to help you construct a winning team. What pushes Jaxon Smith-Njigba near WR1 territory as a rookie? The Pros will tell you!
